title: Key Week 1 Matchups and Our Daily Fantasy Lineup | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck highlight the key fantasy matchups to take advantage of heading into Week 1 (3:30), before crafting their daily fantasy lineup of the week (23:00).
